{
  "_comment": [
    "HOW TO ADD/EDIT MECHANICS:",
    "",
    "Each mechanic has 'strats' — a list of named strategy options.",
    "The user picks one active strat per fight in the plugin Settings tab.",
    "All mechanics in that fight will show that strat's image.",
    "",
    "Fields per mechanic:",
    "  slug        - internal ID (not shown in URL, just for reference)",
    "  label       - name shown in the plugin UI (e.g. 'Toxic Act 1')",
    "  triggerTime - seconds into fight when the image pops up (0 = manual only)",
    "  strats      - list of named strat options, each with:",
    "                  name  = label shown in the strat selector (e.g. 'Hector')",
    "                  image = EXACT filename from wtfdig URL",
    "",
    "To get the filename: go to wtfdig.info, right-click an image → Copy image address.",
    "Take everything after the last slash. E.g.:",
    "  https://wtfdig.info/74/m12s/p1-toxic-act1-dps-zoomed.webp",
    "                              ↑ fight id    ↑ this is the filename",
    "",
    "The first strat in the list is the default until the user changes it.",
    "After editing: rebuild the plugin, then Settings → Reset / Regenerate Community Strats."
  ],
